### VNDS For VR
A port of the VNDS engine to Unity for use with the Gear VR/Oculus Rift

### About
TBA

### Usage
TBA

### Download
Best way would be to grab the repo and run through Unity right now. To run with your Gear VR you will need to replace the oculus sig file in the plugins folder. Please see https://developer.oculus.com/osig/ to generate your signature file based on your device.

### Authors and Contributors
Right now it's looking like it's just me. Looking for additional authors more versed in audio encoding in order to support more formats on the fly. 

### Support or Contact
Shoot me a message on Github.
